5.1. The Service stores personal data of users in accordance with its internal rules.
5.2. The user's personal information will be kept confidential, except when the user voluntarily provides information about himself for public access to an unlimited number of persons.
5.3. The service has the right to transfer the user's personal data to third parties in the following cases:
5.3.1. If the user agrees to such actions;
5.3.2. If the transfer is necessary for the user to use a certain service or to fulfill a certain agreement or contract with the user;
5.3.3. If the transfer is provided in accordance with the procedure established by law;
5.3.4. In the case of a sale of the Service, the acquirer assumes all obligations to comply with the terms of this policy with respect to the personal data it receives;
5.3.5. In order to ensure the possibility of protecting the rights and legal interests of the service administration or third parties in cases where the user violates the terms of use of the service.
5.4. The processing of the user's personal data is carried out in any legal way, including in information systems of personal data using automation tools or without using such tools. Processing of personal data of users is carried out in accordance with the current legislation of the Republic of Uzbekistan.
5.5. In case of loss or disclosure of personal data, the service administration will notify the user about the loss or disclosure of personal data.
5.6. The service administration takes the necessary organizational and technical measures to protect the user's personal data from unauthorized or accidental access, destruction, modification, blocking, copying, distribution, as well as other illegal actions of third parties.
5.7. The service administration together with the user will take all necessary measures to prevent losses or other negative consequences caused by the loss or disclosure of the user's personal data.

